@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jijvhr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.56) + (v2 + 0.77 / tmp + 0.67)) / 0.70)
    v1 = 0.97
    v0 = (0.76 / wp.exp((v2 + 0.03 / v1 + 0.32)))
    tmp = (0.11 - ((v2 + 0.20 / tmp + 0.84) * wp.abs(v2 + 0.93)))
    data[tid] = v0
